data.title: Bitcoin Vs. Ethereum And The Flippening Lubin Predicts
data.description: Joe Lubin predicts Ethereum will flip Bitcoin. This analysis explains ETH’s utility loop, Bitcoin’s scarcity, and why money is entering a multi-form future.
data.author: Jon Helgi Egilsson
data.keywords: Ethereum flippening,ETH vs BTC,Ethereum vs Bitcoin,Will Ethereum flip Bitcoin,ETH flip Bitcoin,Joe Lubin Ethereum prediction,Ethereum utility,Bitcoin scarcity,Ethereum monetary model
